00:03:43.550 --> 00:03:45.150
I almost got beaten by my deskmate a few times.

00:03:45.150 --> 00:03:47.016
This really takes me back.

00:03:47.016 --> 00:03:49.283
This pen works even better

00:03:49.283 --> 00:03:50.466
 with Lenovo's Smart Documents.

00:03:50.466 --> 00:03:51.199
For example,

00:03:51.199 --> 00:03:52.533
 if you come across something you don't understand,

00:03:52.533 --> 00:03:53.516
 just circle it 

00:03:53.516 --> 00:03:54.250
and draw a question mark, 

