00:04:09.650 --> 00:04:10.583
It feels just like 

00:04:10.583 --> 00:04:13.416
how I used to write key points on sticky notesand

00:04:13.416 --> 00:04:14.949
 stick them in my books

00:04:14.949 --> 00:04:17.250
